tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_gates (
    gate_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    gate_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    operation VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    effect VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    qubit_index INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE gate_qubit_relation (
    relation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gate_id INT,
    qubit_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (gate_id) REFERENCES quantum_gates(gate_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (qubit_id) REFERENCES qubits(qubit_id)
);
